title: Google honours corona helpers with GIF doodle
description: Google honours corona helpers with GIF doodleOn Twitter, Google India urged the followers to stay at home.
content: After a thankful week, search engine giant Google, on Saturday, honoured all coronavirus helpers with a creative doodle, featuring doctors, nurses, delivery staff, farmers, teachers, researchers, sanitation workers, grocery workers and emergency services work… [+3492 chars]
